# Web3 & DeFi (contracts)

- No unchecked external calls; CEI; document trust model (oracles, admins, upgradability).
- Fuzz / invariants for financial logic; bound inputs in tests.
- No private keys or production RPC URLs in source; use env + CI secrets.
- Prefer OpenZeppelin patterns; align compiler/EVM version with `tech-stack.md`.
- Delegate product UI and APIs to fullstack agent; protocol economics with `defi-protocol-engineer`.
